{"tid":1509604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好辛苦，現階段仲有咩做到？","createTime":"2019-08-27T01:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T02:21:54.000Z","uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"36785a4def3bd7419780d2cdb615a02bffd685df","tid":1509604,"uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"自問發夢有上過前線幫勇武<br />\n和理非又做過晒<br />\n區議會選舉亦都出工出力<br />\n但係3個月啦，仆街政府唔係不聞不問就係逃避回應，警犬繼續濫權濫暴，日日開個濕鳩講大話記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最難頂係屋企兩老都係藍，番到去聽埋佢地講瘋言瘋語，信黨報信cctvb都唔信落過前線既我，個心真係好攰，係屋企真係寧願鎖埋自己間房算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔會尋死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003ba66ccb09a90b72b24ec7baac518472a413a8","tid":1509604,"uid":157450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:53:47.000Z","msg":"堅持"},{"pid":"ab267becfbca7c5227743f13e1ef7c63b3bb733b","tid":1509604,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=9cd764e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=f5d73145\" data-auto-link targ