/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=0ca9de9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102458676557543%2Fposts%2F1582783125191750%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=2c09bb2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo</a><br />\n將窗嗌口號變成一種普及的生活方式，會好大感染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyn9vh9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcyn9vh9.png&h=f1d434e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tn6aZUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTn6aZUy.jpg&h=d0ae64af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e16079095726aae46b861a05cc748a5f050d2df9","tid":1509604,"uid":41353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:56:12.000Z","msg":"唔需要爭取廢老認同，佢同你成為屋企人只係一個抽籤出黎的結果。如果覺得累就唔好理幾日，瘋狂煲劇，打機咩都好，做下其他野"},{"pid":"cca0f0a8a43e2edaa1433d14bf84ce6bc01f25de","tid":1509604,"uid":266621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:57:55.000Z","msg":"繼續做好自己就夠, 應該要做既野就做"},{"pid":"bbc4a8a5d0b784a0e1b1e1f78e8057412d094eb7","tid":1509604,"uid":171450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:59:08.000Z","msg":"盡快搬走先，林鄭佢唯一一句講得岩既就係打消耗戰，睇下邊邊頂唔順先，加油呀"},{"pid":"27325606462e695d123a9d8448167b9ef8e1596c","tid":1509604,"uid":1525